=============================================================
  GPRTool Test File — Kalamunda Mixed-Use Tower
  DXF R2010 | Units: metres | Origin: site centroid
  
  BUILDING DESCRIPTION
  --------------------
  8-storey mixed-use development, Kalamunda foothills, Perth
  Site area:        ~12,400 m2
  
  Storeys:
    FL 00 (Z=0.0)    Ground — commercial podium + planting
    FL 01 (Z=4.2)    Commercial podium roof / podium garden
    FL 02 (Z=4.2)    Residential floors 3-5 base
    FL 03-05         Residential (stepped back, north face)
    FL 06 (Z=18.6)   Sky garden terrace — open planted deck
    FL 07-08         Penthouse residential
    ROOF (Z=28.2)    Roof garden
  
  Green elements (for GPR):
    - Ground planting beds (GROUND_PLANTING layer)
    - Sky garden terrace at FL06, Z=18.6m (SKY_GARDEN layer)
    - Roof garden at Z=28.2m (ROOF_GARDEN layer)
  
  LAYER GUIDE
  -----------
  SITE_BOUNDARY        Closed LWPOLYLINE — site perimeter at Z=0
  GROUND_PLANTING      Closed LWPOLYLINEs — planting beds at Z=0
  PODIUM_FOOTPRINT     Closed LWPOLYLINE — FL1-2 footprint at Z=0
  PODIUM_MASS          3DFACE — podium walls Z=0 to Z=8.4
  RESIDENTIAL_FOOTPRINT  Closed LWPOLYLINE — FL3-5 footprint at Z=8.4
  RESIDENTIAL_MASS     3DFACE — residential walls Z=8.4 to Z=18.6
  SKY_GARDEN           Closed LWPOLYLINE — sky garden deck at Z=18.6
  PENTHOUSE_FOOTPRINT  Closed LWPOLYLINE — FL7-8 footprint at Z=18.6
  PENTHOUSE_MASS       3DFACE — penthouse walls Z=18.6 to Z=28.2
  ROOF_GARDEN          Closed LWPOLYLINE — roof garden at Z=28.2
  TERRAIN_CONTOURS     3D POLYLINEs — 2m contours, Z=elevation AHD
  
  STOREY HEIGHTS: 4.2m commercial / 3.6m residential
  COORDINATE SYSTEM: local metres, right-hand, Z=up
  CRS NOTE: no georeferencing — user aligns to site in GPRTool
=============================================================

